<section id="import-phyphox-data" class="level1">
<h1>Import Phyphox Data</h1>
<p>It is super easy to get a dataset to work with from phyphox.</p>
<ol type="1">
<li>collect your data.</li>
<li>In the data collection screen click the three dots in the upper right corner and click export data.</li>
<li>select <strong>CSV (Comma, decimal point)</strong> or anything you want but that one is easy to use.</li>
<li>Download the csv file and move it to you rcode project working directory.</li>
</ol>
<p>Here is some data I collected this morning on my way to class.</p>
