<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="welcome-to-my-pages."><strong>Welcome to my pages.</strong></h2>
<div class="quarto-figure quarto-figure-center">
<figure class="figure">
<p><img src="https://homepage.sugerplum.uk/posts/welcome/images/sugerplum.uk-01.jpg" class="img-fluid figure-img" width="526"></p>
<figcaption>\ Sugerplum: The American Pitbull Terrier</figcaption>
</figure>
